NEXT:
* Soft fork of yabar
* Better window title handling
* Variable with block support
* Spacing feature for internal blocks
* New internal blocks:
  - load average
  - battery charge


0.4.0 (2016-04-08):
* Support for dynamic color change
* Prefix and suffix options for internal blocks
* New internal blocks:
  - window title
  - workspaces
  - CPU load
  - disk I/O
  - RAM usage (memory)
  - network usage (bandwith)
  - uptime
  - temperature (thermal)
  - display brightness
  - time and date

0.3.0 (2016-03-24):
* Support for justifying text left, center and right
* Support for bar borders


0.2.3 (2016-03-21):
* Changed license from ISC to MIT
